{
  "page": "Four Storms",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png/350px-The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"438\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png/525px-The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2c/The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png/700px-The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_four_storms_by_viscardiac.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Four Storms, by viscardiac ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Four Storms</b> was the nickname used to refer to the four daughters of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Borros_Baratheon\" title=\"Borros Baratheon\">Borros Baratheon</a> and his wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Elenda_Baratheon\" title=\"Elenda Baratheon\">Elenda Caron</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to Lord Borros, his daughters sometimes fought with each other, but he saw to it that they always made peace afterward.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Four_Storms\">The Four Storms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Four_Storms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Four Storms\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Cassandra_Baratheon\" title=\"Cassandra Baratheon\">Cassandra</a>, the eldest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maris_Baratheon\" title=\"Maris Baratheon\">Maris</a>, the second eldest and the cleverest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_a_son_for_a_son.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Baratheon\" title=\"Ellyn Baratheon\">Ellyn</a>, the third or fourth born.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Floris_Baratheon\" title=\"Floris Baratheon\">Floris</a>, the third or fourth born and the prettiest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Four_Storms&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=